BEGIN CRUMB
v=1.3
kind=task
title=Carry executable validation intent with the handoff
source=claude.agent
project=web-app
---
[goal]
Validate that the receiving agent honors a specific policy before running.

[context]
- The caller already ran the tests.
- The receiver must confirm it cannot shell-exec before proceeding.

[constraints]
- Do not execute [script] bodies in untrusted runtimes

[script]
@type: weave
@action: validate
---
agent.can("shell-exec") -> false
agent.must("run_tests") -> true
END CRUMB
